Usage:
  kubectl annotate [--overwrite] (-f FILENAME | TYPE NAME) KEY_1=VAL_1 ... KEY_N=VAL_N [--resource-version=version] [options]

Use "kubectl options" for a list of global command-line options (applies to all commands).
